I’ve stared typing this multiple times now; not knowing how to put all of these feelings into the right words!… 

I am so #grateful to everyone who supported the first-annual HOLIDAY FANTASIA (A Celebration Of The Arts). Our heart’s desire was to honor the immense and diverse #talent of our community while benefiting two amazing causes that hold special meaning to both Ray and I, @bowtiekids and the ‘A Foster-Care Christmas’ program (in partnership with JFOY). We have a passion for supporting #youth, especially within the Foster-Care and Foster-To-Adopt programs. Both our families are blended with beautiful humans that were brought together by the #FosterSystem. 

When we moved down to #FortLauderdale last year, we met @thebowtiegurl along with her beautiful wife, @traceyprescod , and were introduced to BowTie Kids. Our three children all deal with #EhlersDanlos syndrome which affects connective tissue, primarily the skin, joints, and blood vessel walls. BowTie Kids’ mission is to support kids dealing with chronic pain and their families. It was like the universe directed us to Karen, so we could get plugged in right away and help #support our new #community. 

Bringing artists together in a collaborative way is something I love doing and, in my opinion, has the potential to yield something breathtakingly beautiful. Sunday’s event is proof of exactly that! Our community is blessed with so many talented #artists and #performers, many of whom donated their time and their gifts to make this dream of mine a reality. Words alone do not suffice in expressing my gratitude. #ThankYou!

AND I would be remiss if failed to acknowledge two incredible human beings, without whom, this show would not have been possible! My incomparable Co-Host, the one and only, talented, tall, tank-like, treasure… Miss @varlajeanmerman! …and my loving husband who consistently helps reel me in when my ideas become too lofty, but nurtures my creativity with his support and patience every day, @rayboston. Love you guys:) 

Until next year… #HAPPYHOLIDAYS everyone!!!
#GladToGiveGala with my man @rayboston
